section.div: This repository contains a food classification website featuring a model trained on the Food101 dataset using Transfer Learning to classify food images.
This repository consists of various concepts of Deep Learning covered using PyTorch.

Hi, I'm Anas Hasan, a passionate CSE student with a keen interest in AIML. This profile showcases my journey in the tech world, featuring a variety of projects, from deep learning applications like image classification and object detection to NLP experiments. Feel free to explore my repositories for in-depth insights into my work and contributions!

This repository is dedicated to showcasing various NLP projects and experiments. Each project focuses on solving real-world problems using NLP techniques, from text classification to sentiment analysis. Whether you're exploring spam detection, fake news detection, or other NLP applications.
This repository focuses on working with FastAPI and making use of JWT Authentication, integrating background tasks with Redis and celery and checking API availability through RestFox.
